caption.p: Mean Q10 values for kinematic-velocity in each of the three invasive-fish species. Note that except for the mean Q10 values for lower-jaw rotation in the Mayan cichlid and lionfish, all Q10 values of kinematic velocity were significantly less than the expected Q10 value of 2.0 for fish feeding at 20 °C and 30 °C. Error bars indicate standard error of the mean.
